title: (Recruiting Members for club Moose) Low Elo players welcome
body: I want to fill my club with all the Meeses that want to join, I am a bronze ranked player and im basically looking for people to play ranked with who are around the same level and want to team together. all Low Elo Bronze/Silver players welcome, add my IGN: SlipperyMoose96

replies.body: Ill play ranked 5's with you Im gold though so i hope that is okay? main adc/mid
i am in legogoliath is my ign
I am willing to join if you like and tbh, you don't have to tell us your in game name, it's your username for all comments :)
